  • Aashirvaad Atta with Multigrains is made with the choicest grains which provides you and your family wholesome nutrition
  • Aashirvaad Atta with Multigrains is a blend of 6 natural grains – wheat, maize, soya, Chana, oats, psyllium husk
  • India’s No. 1 Atta brand, Aashirvaad Atta with Multigrains is Made with love in India with the grains sourced from the fields across the country
  • Aashirvaad Atta with Multigrains is high in fibre which aids in digestion and ensures a healthy gut
  • This multigrain flour is rich in proteins, vitamins, minerals and fibre which ensures a fit, active and healthy life
  • There is no compromise in taste as the rotis made from Aashirvaad Atta with Multigrains are smooth, soft and tasty
